The code assumes that we are working with pvcs in a unix environment(actually 
that we are not using a mapped drive to point to the db eg. not p:\PVCSdb) and 
therefore does not create the folder structure we need to check out files to.
I have included code below that will solve the problem. Feel free to use it.


